WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.790 --> 00:00:05.642
The average TV viewer spends over three
hours a day in front of their TV set.

00:00:05.642 --> 00:00:08.914
You would expect by now we would have
solved the problem of providing a simple

00:00:08.914 --> 00:00:11.850
interface to find and
engage with our favorite content.

00:00:11.850 --> 00:00:15.860
Watching TV should be easy,
but way too often it's not.

00:00:15.860 --> 00:00:20.010
In this lesson, you'll learn all
about Google Cast, Android TV, and

00:00:20.010 --> 00:00:23.710
how to use them to give your users
a great experience that they deserve,

00:00:23.710 --> 00:00:24.400
with your content.

